  <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Security</h1>
  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">Last updated: September 25, 2025</p>

  <p class="mb-6">
    This tool sends <span class="font-semibold">infra coaching emails</span> to your engineers. <span class="font-semibold">No logins, dashboards,</span> or <span class="font-semibold">SSO.</span>
  </p>

  <p class="mb-6">
    Every Monday, a cron job starts private email threads with your engineers about SEV-1 prevention. The Rails app receives a webhook when they reply, and sends back the results of a few GPT prompts.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-6">
    <span class="font-semibold">No customer data.</span> If users type it anyway, the LLC has <a href="/replicate-coi.pdf" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-semibold">$1M E&O</a> + <a href="/replicate-coi.pdf" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-semibold">$1M Cyber</a> coverage.
  </p>

  <div class="mb-6">
  </div>

  <p class="mb-6">
    You will receive a <a href="/replicate-msa-dpa.pdf" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-semibold">pre-signed MSA/DPA</a> during the <a href="/billing" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-semibold">trial period</a>. No RFPs, redlines, or vendor portals.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-6">Liability is capped at <span class="font-semibold">5x the fees</span> paid across your <span class="font-semibold">entire contract</span>, even if multi-year. Exclusions are uncapped: willful misconduct, gross negligence, IP infringement, and confidentiality breaches.</p>

